Email,Center,Pro,is,an,email,management,service,for,customer,service,teams,Because,it,is,entirely,web,based,employees,can,log,in,and,work,from,anywhere,The,service,provides,a,variety,of,useful,features,including,the,ability,to,save,answers,to,FAQs,as,one,click,templates,link,email,conversations,with,cases,in,a,bug,tracking,system,measure,email,traffic,both,in,and,out,of,the,system,and,view,a,complete,record,of,every,action,taken,on,any,email,Email,Center,Pro,also,provides,services,for,managing,employees,Administrators,can,add,new,employees,assign,permissions,assign,emails,to,specific,employees,and,keep,track,of,each,individual,s,workload,and,response,times,A,spam,filter,comes,already,in,place,and,the,intensity,of,the,screening,can,be,adjusted,Many,of,Email,Center,Pro,s,features,are,accessible,using,a,RESTful,interface